{"tid":122453,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人幾個屋企人討厭嘅壞習慣","createTime":"2017-02-16T04:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T05:14:41.000Z","uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2646afbd23156e43bf831969ff4d8db9d364cacc","tid":122453,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"成日搵啲嘢頂住個櫃門，要攞嗰陣話佢頂住晒，會話返你搬走再攞唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢地啲嘢放喺邊，永遠剩係會籠統咁答你，例如喺廚房問佢啲密實袋放邊，會答返你喺廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好多禮貌上嘅嘢，喺街大聲講電話講到鬧交咁、出街嗰陣講嘢單單打打等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210099e90cce6288e9eb9ba6deb83676002bdae8","tid":122453,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日搵啲嘢頂住個櫃門，要攞嗰陣話佢頂住晒，會話返你搬走再攞唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問佢地啲嘢放喺邊，永遠剩係會籠統咁答你，例如喺廚房問佢啲密實袋放邊，會答返你喺廚房</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好多禮貌上嘅嘢，喺街大聲講電話講到鬧交咁、出街嗰陣講嘢單單打打等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母仲搞笑<br />\n問佢啲野係邊<br />\n佢話「係你面前！」<br />\n<br />\n但面前係成大個廚房<br />\n再問佢就話「係！你！眼！前！」<br />\n一係就話「係你手到呀係咪要拎埋俾你呀？」<br />\n<br />\n根本唔係答緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢覺得你唔知係你錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6866fd3ce4f62afdb3b18a62be3abf4e1b8d4016","tid":122453,"uid":67047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:06:55.000Z","msg":"老豆成日出街唔帶鎖匙,每次都喺我打緊機嘅時候先返嚟要我去開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c8ce7d43f751cb0865bad426736e6bba8a6a82","tid":122453,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"沖完涼會好有手尾咁關熱水爐<br />\n利申:儲水式"}]}